====Usage notes====
* There is no explicit limit, but the word ''boat'' usually refers to a relatively small watercraft, smaller than a [[ship]] but larger than a [[dinghy]]. It is also the normal designation for a submarine (however large), and also for [[laker]]s (ships used in the [[Great Lakes]] trade in North America).

